1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,170
=Episode 23=

12
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,900
Uncle-in-law, your sudden approach

13
00:01:30,620 --> 00:01:32,420
makes me rather uneasy.

14
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:33,980
You're not uneasy.

15
00:01:34,580 --> 00:01:36,460
You're calm and composed.

16
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:39,100
Tonight, we're merely
competing in speed.

17
00:01:43,140 --> 00:01:44,940
It seems you are faster.

18
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:45,899
I bet you took down

19
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:47,540
my shadow guards.

20
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:49,940
I only wish to know

21
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:52,499
why I must die
at the hands of my own kin.

22
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:54,020
Enough nonsense.

23
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:56,540
You already knew my identity.

24
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:58,820
Don't speak of kinship.

25
00:01:59,140 --> 00:02:01,380
My aunt now carries your child.

26
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:05,620
Does that count for nothing?

27
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:12,819
Your aunt has miscarried.

28
00:02:12,820 --> 00:02:14,420
If her life is in danger,

29
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:16,420
then we are no longer kin.

30
00:02:17,060 --> 00:02:19,100
Zhen Xiuyi has already
let go of the hatred.

31
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:20,299
You should stop clinging

32
00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:22,020
to the grudges of the past!

33
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:30,940
Brother!

34
00:02:32,460 --> 00:02:33,580
Brother!

35
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:34,780
Stop!

36
00:02:36,260 --> 00:02:38,100
Wuju was harmed because of me.

37
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:41,060
How can I still go on living?

38
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:43,260
Brother!

39
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:45,740
Xiao Man.

40
00:02:47,875 --> 00:02:48,911
Put the blade down.

41
00:02:48,912 --> 00:02:50,152
I beg you.

42
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,140
Brother.

43
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:55,940
Uncle-in-law.

44
00:02:56,460 --> 00:02:58,220
I was lying just now.

45
00:02:58,340 --> 00:02:59,940
Aunt is in labour.

46
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:01,579
If you go now, there's still time.

47
00:03:01,580 --> 00:03:03,299
Live once for yourself.

48
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,420
Brother.

49
00:03:05,337 --> 00:03:06,697
Please live on.

50
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:09,620
Live to see the one you love.

51
00:03:13,020 --> 00:03:14,379
Why are you still standing there?

52
00:03:14,380 --> 00:03:15,740
Go, now.

53
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:17,580
Aren't you going to punish me?

54
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:20,139
I promised Xiao Man

55
00:03:20,140 --> 00:03:22,220
I would spare her entire family.

56
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:24,700
Now that no one stands in the way,

57
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:28,180
whether you're guilty is
for Aunt to decide.

58
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:34,420
She really is in labour.

59
00:03:37,540 --> 00:03:39,300
Go, quickly.

60
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,540
Xiao Man...

61
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:55,580
She's given birth.

62
00:03:56,100 --> 00:03:58,020
A lovely little girl.

63
00:03:59,580 --> 00:04:01,060
She's still waiting for you.

64
00:04:01,580 --> 00:04:03,340
Don't disappoint her again.

65
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,740
You're awake.

66
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:30,020
I'll ask you one thing.

67
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:34,940
All these years...

68
00:04:37,137 --> 00:04:39,737
Was it all just a means to have revenge?

69
00:05:00,740 --> 00:05:05,539
Wuju, on the day we were married,

70
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:07,740
you were honest with me.

71
00:05:08,587 --> 00:05:10,107
But I wasn't.

72
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:11,419
Now,

73
00:05:11,420 --> 00:05:14,300
I can finally be honest with you.

74
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:19,980
Sun Gong is Zhen Muyu.

75
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:22,579
He's the boy who once declared

76
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:24,980
he would marry no one but you.

77
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:27,219
And the young man

78
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:29,540
who became your Prince Consort.

79
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:38,220
This is what Zhen Muyu
looked like as an adult.

80
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:59,580
You and I

81
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:02,020
were never meant to be.

82
00:06:09,662 --> 00:06:11,542
I've wronged you.

83
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:45,020
Sun Gong has taken poison!

84
00:06:55,620 --> 00:06:57,620
Whoever bites into the middle first

85
00:06:58,220 --> 00:06:59,540
wins.

86
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:01,700
Then, I won't hold back.

87
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,540
Just call her Princess.

88
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:14,420
There's no need to call her family.

89
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:17,420
I'll soon sever all ties with her.

90
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:20,460
Do you really believe that yourself?

91
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:26,340
Ever since we met on the day
of the military examinations,

92
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:28,860
I made up my mind

93
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:31,020
not to wait for him anymore.

94
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:33,379
Because I had found

95
00:07:33,380 --> 00:07:35,860
my own destiny.

96
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:40,540
From that moment on,

97
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:43,420
I didn't care
what became of Zhen Muyu.

98
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:46,940
I only knew
how kind Sun Gong was to me.

99
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:09,220
Muyu...

100
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:22,820
Muyu...

101
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:34,580
His Majesty and I never meant
to hold you accountable.

102
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:38,900
Why go this far?

103
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:50,420
Our daughter...

104
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:15,820
I don't want to die.

105
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:19,540
I don't want to die.

106
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:22,380
The imperial physician is on the way.

107
00:09:22,540 --> 00:09:24,060
He'll be here any moment.

108
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:26,900
It's too late.

109
00:09:40,762 --> 00:09:43,282
The hatred was real.

110
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:46,740
But the love was real too.

111
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:51,099
I did think about using you.

112
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:54,340
But I couldn't control my feelings.

113
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:57,900
I love you.

114
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:02,700
I wanted to grow old with you.

115
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:08,220
I wanted to watch our daughter grow up.

116
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:12,620
I've never lived

117
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:15,900
for myself

118
00:10:16,860 --> 00:10:20,270
since I was twelve.

119
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:05,620
Whether you are Sun Gong

120
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:09,380
or Zhen Muyu...

121
00:11:14,625 --> 00:11:16,425
I love you all the same.

122
00:11:20,860 --> 00:11:22,860
I love you all the same.

123
00:11:34,700 --> 00:11:35,939
Your Majesty.

124
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:38,380
Minister Sun passed away at dawn today.

125
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:40,899
Before his death,
he left a letter for Eunuch Xiao Man.

126
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:42,500
Present it at once.

127
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:55,180
(Mujun, my dear sister.)

128
00:11:56,140 --> 00:11:57,500
(This campaign)

129
00:11:58,100 --> 00:12:00,500
(brings me back
to the frontier after twenty years.)

130
00:12:01,620 --> 00:12:03,139
(When I saw
scattered lights flickering)

131
00:12:03,140 --> 00:12:05,140
(beneath the mountain,)

132
00:12:06,020 --> 00:12:08,060
(it felt as though I had rediscovered)

133
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:10,900
(my ambition of
guarding the frontier with Mother.)

134
00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:13,340
(I've also begun
to understand your thoughts.)

135
00:12:14,300 --> 00:12:17,299
(People often speak of
the tens of thousands of troops)

136
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:20,020
(and the frontier citizens
as if they were some vague collective.)

137
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:21,739
(But they are made up of)

138
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:23,740
(countless small families,)

139
00:12:24,140 --> 00:12:25,660
(just like you and me.)

140
00:12:26,087 --> 00:12:28,700
(Everyone is living a real life.)

141
00:12:29,512 --> 00:12:30,912
(If I were to slay His Majesty,)

142
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:32,939
(it would plunge court
and realm into chaos,)

143
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:34,339
(the frontier into turmoil,)

144
00:12:34,340 --> 00:12:37,300
(and bring ruin
to countless soldiers and lands)

145
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:40,300
(To fill the hatred in my heart)

146
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:43,300
(with countless living lives)

147
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:45,780
(would be unforgivable.)

148
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:49,700
(Uncle and I
have already committed grave sins.)

149
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:51,540
(Death would not
be too heavy a price.)

150
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:55,060
(I've failed our parents,)

151
00:12:55,512 --> 00:12:56,632
(And I've failed)

152
00:12:57,500 --> 00:12:59,980
(my wife's love.)

153
00:13:00,740 --> 00:13:04,940
(But what's done cannot be undone.)

154
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:09,460
(I've already taken poison.)

155
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:11,980
(Under the name of regicide,)

156
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:15,620
(I'll use my life to end this hatred.)

157
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:20,100
(I hope you will inherit
(our parents' final legacy.)

158
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:23,180
(This is farewell.)

159
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:24,660
(Your brother,)

160
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:26,340
(Muyu.)
